      <%= image_tag "frontimage2.jpg", :class => "img-responsive" %>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="carousel-caption">
          <h1>Welcome to Tally</h1>
          <p>An cardless loyalty system that effortlessly brings your customers back again and again.</p>
          <p><a class="btn btn-lg btn-primary" href="http://getbootstrap.com">Learn More</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
  <!-- Controls -->
  <a class="left carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" data-slide="prev">
    <span class="icon-prev"></span>
  </a>
  <a class="right carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" data-slide="next">
    <span class="icon-next"></span>
  </a>  
</div>
<!-- /.carousel -->


<!-- Marketing messaging and featurettes
================================================== -->
<!-- Wrap the rest of the page in another container to center all the content. -->

<div class="container marketing">

  <!-- Three columns of text below the carousel -->
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
      <img class="img-circle fit" src="http://ww1.prweb.com/prfiles/2012/02/29/9239098/gI_81293_noshlist-armoractive.jpg" alt="Image">
      <h2>The Tally kiosk</h2>
      <p>A sleek and simple interface allowing customers to check-in to your establishment on each visit and earn loyalty rewards. Gather a database of customer contact details.</p>
      <p><a class="btn darkbase" href="#">View details »</a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
      <img class="img-circle fit" src="http://brucepowerdirect.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/dashboard-270x180.png" alt="Image">
      <h2>Customer analytics</h2>
      <p>Understand the visiting patterns of your most valued customers using Tally's unique analytics platform, and find new ways to connect with and retain them.</p>
      <p><a class="btn darkbase" href="#">View details »</a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
      <img class="img-circle fit" src="http://ijustneedhelpbookkeeping.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2012/12/happy-customer.jpeg" alt="Image">
      <h2>Marketing, simplified</h2>
      <p>Choose a customised email marketing plan that completely removes the pain from building relationships with your clients.</p>
      <p><a class="btn darkbase" href="#">View details »</a></p>
    </div>
  </div><!-- /.row -->


  <!-- START THE FEATURETTES -->

  <hr class="featurette-divider">

  <div class="featurette">
    <img class="featurette-image img-circle pull-right" src="http://placehold.it/512" alt="Image">
    <h2 class="featurette-heading">Reward your customers. <span class="text-muted">Everybody wins.</span></h2>
    <p class="lead">Customers check-in using their email address each time they visit and are told how many visits they have left before they earn their loyalty reward. No cards, no stamps. </p>
  </div>

  <hr class="featurette-divider">

  <div class="featurette">
    <img class="featurette-image img-circle pull-left" src="http://placehold.it/512" alt="Image">
    <h2 class="featurette-heading">Understand your customers. <span class="text-muted">Study their visiting patterns.</span></h2>
    <p class="lead">Tally collects data everytime your customers checkin, and relays it to you in a sleek dashboard. You can monitor how regularly your customers visit, and be notified if a regular hasn't returned for a while.</p>
  </div>

  <hr class="featurette-divider">

  <div class="featurette">
    <img class="featurette-image img-circle pull-right" src="http://placehold.it/512" alt="Image">
    <h2 class="featurette-heading">Engage your customers. <span class="text-muted">Build an email list of your most valued customers and keep them informed.</span></h2>
    <p class="lead">Doing a special offer today? Let your customers know. Have a new product? Let your customers know. The possiblities are endless.</p>
  </div>

  <hr class="featurette-divider">

  <!-- /END THE FEATURETTES -->


